I am new to NewsBreak. My ad is pending for a week.  Is there anything I need to do?

Hi Herman, welcome to NewsBreak! If your ad is pending due to it being a new account and not being verified, please provide the following details by emailing adsupport@newsbreak.com with the subject line: Business Verification –
- Company's full address
- Company's legal entity name
- Company's EHID or DUNS number
- Primary contact person's name
- Company's phone number
Once we receive this information, we will conduct a thorough review and update you on your account status. We appreciate your cooperation in maintaining a secure and compliant advertising environment for all our partners. If you have any questions, please don't hesitate to reach out.
I sent it via email just now. I wish someone had asked for this information.

Thank you for sending the information, Herman. I'm sorry for any inconvenience caused. Our team will review your details and update you on your account status as soon as possible. If you have any other questions or need further assistance, feel free to ask!

I had seny my business information along with EIN letter from IRS two days ago.  Do you need anything else from me?  When I can expect my ads to go live?  (While I am not in a hurry, I have to hire my coach Tom Bell to help me out)

Thank you for sending your business information. To proceed with the verification process and have your account approved, please ensure you have provided the following details by emailing adsupport@newsbreak.com with the subject line: Business Verification –
- Company's full address
- Company's legal entity name
- Company's EHID or DUNS number
- Primary contact person's name
- Company's phone number
Once we receive this information, we will conduct a thorough review and update you on your account status. The review process can take a few days, so please be patient. If you have any questions or need further assistance, feel free to reach out.
